metadata.name: Eternal Embrace
metadata.description:
Two hearts enmeshed in sweet embrace,  
With love and passion etched on their face.  
A moment captured, love divine,  
In every caress, in every line.

Their souls, now melded, beat as one,  
A bond unbroken, forever undone.  
The world around them fades away,  
As they cling on, forever to stay.

Oh, sweet Valentine, how you do inspire,  
Love and passion, a fierce burning fire.  
Two lovers, in perpetuity adore,  
In each other's embrace, forevermore.
